'''Galaxy publications''' are adult magazine publishers.<ref>[http://www.galaxypublications.co.uk/ Galaxy publications - Official website]</ref> Their main offices are located in [[Witham]], [[Essex]], [[England]].<ref>[http://www.hotfroguk.co.uk/Companies/Galaxy-Publications-Limited HotfrogUK]</ref><ref>[http://publishing.zibb.co.uk/profile/galaxy+publications+ltd/gb/essex/witham/cm8+3sz/23427783 ]</ref> Their most notable publications include [[Fiesta (magazine)|Fiesta]],<ref>Fiesta, Volume 43, Issue 9. ISSN: 02651270</ref><ref>[http://www.fiesta.co.uk/ Fiesta magazine official website]</ref> [[Knave (magazine)|Knave]],<ref>[http://www.knave.co.uk/ Knave official website]</ref> Ravers DVD<ref>[http://www.raversdvd.co.uk/ Ravers DVD official website]</ref> and Just18.<ref>[http://www.just-18.co.uk/ Just18 official website]</ref>
